// CoreStack Monorepo Workspace.
// Ties the per-provider Go modules together sp `go build ./...`, `go test`, and editor tooling work across the repo without changing any module's own path or go.mod.
// Each provider remains an independent module - this file only affects local multi-module development

// The modules pin different Go version (aws: 1.23, azure: 1.22, gcp: 1.23). The workspace go directive must be >= the highest, so it is set to 1.23.
// Build each module with its own toolchain if you need to honor a lower pin.
go 1.23

use (
   ./gcp
)

//./aws
//./azure